query:
/*+ NoHashJoin(q tq s) */ select count(*)
from tag_question AS tq
inner join question AS q
on tq.question_id = q.id AND q.score >= 0 AND q.score <= 5
inner join site AS s
on tq.site_id = s.site_id AND q.site_id = s.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('physics')
inner join tag AS t
on tq.tag_id = t.id AND t.site_id = s.site_id AND t.name IN ('atomic-physics',
'differentiation',
'electric-current',
'heisenberg-uncertainty-principle',
'inertial-frames',
'material-science',
'nuclear-physics',
'quantum-electrodynamics',
'reflection',
'soft-question',
'solid-state-physics',
'tensor-calculus',
'torque',
'universe');
